properties.sfomuseum:author: United Kingdom Air Ministry
properties.sfomuseum:description: Volume 1Orange paper cover with blue cord binding containing looseleaf sheets of paper. Issued to provide information on the construction, use and maintenance of instruments used in aeroplanes and of instruments used on the ground associated with those aeroplanes. Sections 1 - 11 and General Notes on Instrument Repair. Sections: Indicators, Gauges, Thermometers, Altimeters, Levels, Calibrators, Recorders, Compasses, Navigational Instruments, Computing Instruments, Breathing Apparatus. A few illustrations and diagrams.
